      <title>汉莎航空因票价低迷下调利润目标，并将削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/lufthansa-cuts-profit-goal-on-weak-fares-starts-savings-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国汉莎航空集团下调了全年利润预期，并警告称，由于面临单位成本上升和机票价格下跌等问题，其同名德国子公司实现收支平衡将“愈发困难”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/lufthansa-cuts-profit-goal-on-weak-fares-starts-savings-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 10:32:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
